      "index": 0,
      "text": "My analysis of the recovered briefcase is that it contains an advanced Star League personal interstellar communications device, which is a lot more reassuring than the alternative of it being a 'null weapon'.\n\nHowever, the device appears to be only partially functioning since it can't transmit, or at least I couldn't find a way since I am no expert in this kind of technology.",
