    {
      "idRef": {
        "id": "9cb229fa109e5d77ae2d9e1c"
      },
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Even if it's just a communications device, the potential implications are quite large... ComStar has currently the monopoly of space communications because everyone else has lost practical knowledge of translating the Kearny-Fuchida equations into functioning HPG stations.\n\nThis black box is a mortal blow to their business.",
